To use this cmake project:

1) Clone the repository:
   git clone git://gitorious.org/pclsuperbuild/pclsuperbuild.git PCLSuperBuild
2) Create a build directory
   mkdir PCLSuperBuild-build
3) Configure the build
   cd PCLSuperBuild-build
   cmake ../PCLSuperBuild
4) Build PCL and its requisites
   make
